# PR #8371: PS-59856 Add switching menus handle with Observables that can be canc…
**Tipo:** feature
**Branch:** `wip/Abel/PS-59856` → `main`

## Descripción
Add switching menus handle with Observables that can be cancelled and add a provisional dummy iframe when a component is been loaded instead an iframe .

## Feedback de reviewers
[Comentario en Core/Web Layer/WebUI/ps-ng/src/app/Settings/container/settings-container.page.ts:71 por @kcostenbader]: Won't the variable be destroyed after the goes out of scope? Or does the subscription keep it alive?
[Comentario en Core/Web Layer/WebUI/ps-ng/src/app/Settings/container/settings-container.page.ts:71 por @ValdezAbel]: I remember that PR or feature was postponed, but just to answer The variable   navigateTo$ will be a live until  goes out of scope. But  the subscription will be a live until component be destroyed.

